      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROBIN CARGO (3) has a strong record this trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. In the money last time at this track (19.80) in a Grade 5, finishing a 2 length third. Has the ability and should feature. VERY BEST BUDDY (5) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (19.79) at this track behind Dam Panama in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to be in this for a long way. LUMEAH MONTE (7) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at Temora over 330m behind Sonali (19.39) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. Worth another chance. MARVELLOUS MEL (1) can measure up with the right run.",
